{"word":"Rabbah","slug":"rabbah","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Rabbah</b> <a href=\"#/H7237\">H7237</a> <br/> 1. Called Rabbath:<br/> - A city east of the Jordan, originally belonging to the Ammonites<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=13&verse=25'>Jos 13:25</a> <br/> - Bedstead of the giant Og kept at<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=3&verse=11'>Deu 3:11</a> <br/> - Taken by David<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=11&verse=1'>2Sa 11:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=12&verse=31'>2Sa 12:31</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=20&verse=3'>1Ch 20:3</a> <br/> - Possessed again by the Ammonites; prophesied against<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=49&verse=3'>Jer 49:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=21&verse=20'>Eze 21:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=25&verse=5'>Eze 25:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=1&verse=14'>Amo 1:14</a> <br/> 2. A city in Judah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=15&verse=60'>Jos 15:60</a>"}]}